#### Rule Configuration ####

"field": which field this rule applies to , "*" for all fields
"operation": CONTAINS, EQUAL, UNEQUAL, GREATER, LESS, GEQ, LEQ
"compare": Request Header field
"value": value to compare with request header field

Optional: 
	"method": HEAD, POST, PUT, GET, DELETE, and the wildcard *


Maybe ?????

permission: operation when the condition is met

ALLOW_READ: only allow read if the condition is met
DENY_READ: deny read permission to the field
ALLOW_WRITE:
DENY_WRITE:
